Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.46,0:00:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月亮好美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個難道是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告白……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.38,0:00:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.25,0:00:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小幸 告白是要對著這個人做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 對吧祐君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那簡直就像是對我…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是向你們兩人告白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.76,0:00:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡透子 喜歡祐君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我終於說出口了 多虧了祐君才說了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也能對著祐君說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天月亮很美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小幸 感覺我好像還是不太…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.53,0:00:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透子 今後也像之前一樣 好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯……嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天月亮很美！
Comment: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第10集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:35.00,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(976,710)\blur10}「約拿單」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小幸看起來很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小幸 每天都給我發簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡訊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 「為了明天」的簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了明天？
Comment: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的晚飯是什麼呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來來讓我擠擠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天柳學姐也跑步了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 小柳很努力呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陽菜 已經跟透子說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飯後餘興～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鏘鏘{\fscx200}—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陽菜好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有點太豔了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小柳把這個送給你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是雪哉學長稱讚過的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說了不能收下不過還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有沒有 陽菜 很合身哦 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能說一句嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給 咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陽菜…穿著那身…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁熱喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 柳學姐說她要煥然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小柳 果然好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全新的小柳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想見見看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你
Comment: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
