Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:08.43,mail,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(782,600)}本日晴天。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:08.43,mail,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(740,656)}日乃出橋，被子。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.15,mail,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(782,606)}一整天都是晴天。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.15,mail,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(782,662)}冰淇淋店的前面。
